org.json.stream

Class JSONCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.json.stream.JSONCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StructureCollector<JSONObject,JSONArray,JSONObject,JSONArray>

    public final class JSONCollector
extends java.lang.Object
implements StructureCollector<JSONObject,JSONArray,JSONObject,JSONArray>
    Structure collector that creates JSONObject, JSONArray, and JSONObject.NULL instances.

    This collector holds no state, so a singleton is provided.
